Package siminov.hybrid.model


Class Summary
HybridDescriptor Exposes methods to GET and SET Hybrid Descriptor information as per define in HybridDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
HybridDescriptor.Adapter Exposes methods to GET and SET Hybrid Descriptor Adapter information as per define in HybridDescriptor.si.xml file or standalone xml file in application.
HybridDescriptor.Adapter.Handler Exposes methods to GET and SET Hybrid Descriptor Adapter Handler information as per define in HybridDescriptor.si.xml file or in standalone adapter xml file in application.
HybridDescriptor.Adapter.Handler.Parameter Exposes methods to GET and SET Parameter information as per define in HybridDescriptor.si.xml file or in standalone adapter xml file in application.
HybridDescriptor.Adapter.Handler.Return Exposes methods to GET and SET Return information as per define in HybridDescriptor.si.xml file or in standalone adapter xml file in application.
HybridSiminovDatas Exposes methods to GET and SET Siminov Hybrid Datas structure.
HybridSiminovDatas.HybridSiminovData Exposes methods to GET and SET Siminov Hybrid Data structure.
HybridSiminovDatas.HybridSiminovData.HybridSiminovValue Exposes methods to GET and SET Siminov Hybrid Value structure.
LibraryDescriptor Exposes methods to GET and SET Library Descriptor information as per define in LibraryDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
